# MarketPy Frontend — Structure Proposal

Next.js 15 App Router project (TypeScript + Tailwind CSS), created in `./frontend/`.
Connects to the existing FastAPI backend at `http://localhost:8000`.
Auth via JWT stored in `localStorage`. Cart stored in `localStorage`.

---

