## Key Design Decisions

| Decision | Choice | Reason |
|---|---|---|
| Framework | Next.js 15 App Router | User requirement |
| Styling | Tailwind CSS only | User requirement |
| State | `localStorage` | No Redux/Zustand, minimal |
| HTTP | Native `fetch` only | No axios |
| Auth | JWT in `localStorage` | Simple, no cookies |
| Cart | `localStorage` | Server-side cart not required |
| Payments | Mock only | Matches backend |

